name: Sweet Submarine
overview:
Monthly Chocolate Subscription box featuring chocolates from different countries around the world.

The inspiration came from: Coming back from Japan, I brought some fantastic Japanese chocolate cookies for my office. Everyone was absolutely blown away by how good the cookies were. In fact, they were so good that – there was not enough to go around!

The enthusiastic response from my office made me realize something — Not a lot of people gets the opportunity to take the time out to travel the world … nor do they even get the chance to try out all the delicious chocolates there are.

Each box will feature several chocolate types and a large quantity enough for our subscribers to enjoy with their friends and family. Otherwise, chocolate just doesn’t taste as good if you have not enough to share it with.
